items.title: Yanks keep rolling as Monty, HRs roast Birds
items.summary: Didi Gregorius and Greg Bird hit a pair of three-run homers to support Jordan Montgomery's scoreless outing as the Yankees continued to keep the pressure on the division-leading Red Sox, securing a 9-3 victory over the Orioles at Yankee Stadium on Saturday afternoon that marked their 11th win in 14 games.
